CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1941, pg. 10 reads: "Prizewinners At Show Featuring Latest In Hair Fashions - ...Miss Blanche Murray, third prize winner in show at Metropolitan church. North Side conducted by the Beauty Shop Owners.  This was styled by Vivian Cooper of the Harlem Beauty Bar, 93 Fullerton street. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Blanche Murray modeling hairstyle, seen from behind, Harris Studio
